data.title: Category:Princess Margaret of Connaught
data.text:
Margareta (1882-1920), in English often referred to by her original name Margaret, was a Princess of Great Britain and Ireland, daughter of the Duke of Connaught, and by marriage became Crown Princess of Sweden and Duchess of Scania (Skåne).
